cu.explanation_en: Setting amf_ip_address to an invalid IP format (999.999.999.999) will cause AMF connection failure and network unavailability.

du.explanation_en: Setting absoluteFrequencySSB to an out-of-range value (999999999) will cause invalid SSB frequency configuration and synchronization failure.
du.explanation_zh: 將 absoluteFrequencySSB 設定為超出範圍的值 (999999999)，會導致無效的 SSB 頻率配置，並造成同步失敗。
